fields.name: dino
fields.description: Dinos are from an ancient era and will make a unique and engaging pet!

fields.name: lizard
fields.description: Loyal but timid, a lizard will make an excellent pet if you want cool, but quiet!

fields.name: monkey
fields.description: Choosing a monkey will mean a companion for life, but don't try to be their owner! Having a monkey is a partnership.

fields.name: mouse
fields.description: Mice are playful and exciting! Scampering around and chasing them will become a part of your daily routine.

fields.name: tapir
fields.description: Tapirs are a sort of unusual pet. They will love you, but keep an eye out around them! They tend to be troublesome!

fields.name: A E S T H E T I C
fields.description: To get this avatar, have an opalescent or marble pet and gather inspiration at the Rose Garden.

fields.name: Black!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the color black, or unlock the color black in all of the five main species.

fields.name: Blue!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the color blue, or unlock the color blue in all of the five main species.

fields.name: Dino!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the animal Dino, or unlock the pet Dino in all of the five main colors.

fields.name: Divine
fields.description: To get this avatar, complete (without cancelling) fifteen goddess quests in one day.

fields.name: Feeling Blue
fields.description: To get this avatar, have a blue pet, and have five items with 'blue' in the name in your inventory.

fields.name: Green!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the color green, or unlock the color green in all of the five main species.

fields.name: Hi, I'm New!
fields.description: To get this avatar, register for Primaria World.

fields.name: Historic
fields.description: To get this avatar, have a Baroque colored pet, and add an item to your gallery.

fields.name: Lizard!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the animal Lizard, or unlock the pet Lizard in all of the five main colors.

fields.name: Monkey!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the animal Monkey, or unlock the pet Monkey in all of the five main colors.

fields.name: Mouse!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the animal Mouse, or unlock the pet Mouse in all of the five main colors.

fields.name: Pumpkin-Eater
fields.description: To get this avatar, attempt to cheat on a game using Javascript, or use a cheat code.

fields.name: Rainbow
fields.description: To get this avatar, have a pet with ten colors unlocked, including all basic colors.

fields.name: Red!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the color red, or unlock the color red in all of the five main species.

fields.name: Riches!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have at least one million points in the bank.

fields.name: Saved a Penguin
fields.description: To get this avatar, pull up a Six Pack Rings while fishing (awarded randomly).

fields.name: Shhhh!!!
fields.description: To get this avatar, attempt to visit the secrets page.

fields.name: Starry Night
fields.description: To get this avatar, use a starry color potion on your pet from 6pm to 6am.

fields.name: Tapir!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the animal Tapir, or unlock the pet Tapir in all of the five main colors.

fields.name: That Tasted Funny...
fields.description: To get this avatar, use a hunger stat potion on your pet (awarded randomly).

fields.name: Thinker
fields.description: To get this avatar, find a philosophy book while gathering at the Rose Garden.

fields.name: Very Chatty
fields.description: To get this avatar, post 100 replies on the boards.

fields.name: Witch!!!
fields.description: To get this avatar, use a morph potion on your pet (awarded randomly).

fields.name: Yay! Pink!!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have a pink pet and purchase something with 'pink' in the name.

fields.name: Yellow!
fields.description: To get this avatar, have your starting pet be the color yellow, or unlock the color yellow in all of the five main species.

fields.name: Big If True
fields.description: To get this avatar, comment on an announcement post (awarded randomly).

fields.name: Donor
fields.description: To get this avatar, donate to the website.

fields.name: Loafing Around
fields.description: To get this avatar, take a chunk from the Almighty Meatloaf while having at least 25 meatloaves in your inventory.

fields.name: Rulebreaker!
fields.description: To get this avatar, use the machine in the restricted area (awarded randomly).

fields.name: Trading Cards
fields.description: To get this avatar, trade one card with someone for another card in the trade center.

fields.name: Sweet~
fields.description: To get this avatar, have a sprinkle colored pet and feed them a cupcake.

Sprite's Sprouts
fields.description: Full of organic fruits and vegetables, sure to keep your pets well nourished and healthy, even though everything seems to have a very slight coating of dirt.

fields.name: Borders
fields.description: Oh, you're looking for books? You've come to the right place! We are going out of business soon so all books are half price!

fields.name: Traditional Herbs
fields.description: Create the life you were born to live. Ancient fixes proven to cure the mind, body, and spirit. The healing power of nature can get you past any sickness.

fields.name: Alchemist
fields.description: Give your pet new life. Purify and perfect all imperfections. Potions guaranteed to have desirable effects on all pets, young and old.

fields.name: Shop Plush
fields.description: Find your new furry friend at Shop Plush (TM)!

fields.name: Quick Trip
fields.description: Your one-stop-shop for any foods that are "guaranteed" to be good and good for you! No refunds!

fields.name: Basement Games
fields.description: What? No, we don't have... Oh, you're just looking for cards? Yeah, uh, we have those. Yeah. Cards. For playing.

fields.name: Gift Shop
fields.description: Do you need trinkets? Of course you do! How else will people know you visited somewhere if you don't own constant reminders of distant memories?

fields.name: Announcements
fields.description: Find out all the latest happenings on the Primaria announcements boards. Only staff are allowed to post topics, but anyone may comment.

fields.name: General Discussion
fields.description: Any on-topic discussion of Primaria World may be done here. Anyone may create topics as long as they relate to the features of Primaria.

fields.name: Trading and Selling
fields.description: Topics related to the trading, buying, and selling of items belong on this board.

fields.name: Off-Topic Discussion
fields.description: Anything unrelated to Primaria World such as forum games and other discussion belongs on this board.

fields.name: Feedback
fields.description: If you have specific commentary pertinent to the functionality of Primaria World, this is the place to post it. This includes suggestions and other changes you'd like to see made.
